<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idcc8ab461-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70" identifier="/us/usc/t49/s70206"><num value="70206">§ 70206.</num><heading> Savings provision</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this subtitle provides additional authority to regulate or direct private activity on freight networks designated under this subtitle.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idcc8ab462-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/114/94/dA/tVIII/s8001/a">Pub. L. 114–94, div. A, title VIII, § 8001(a)</ref>, <date date="2015-12-04">Dec. 4, 2015</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/129/1612">129 Stat. 1612</ref>, § 70204; renumbered § 70206, <ref href="/us/pl/117/58/dB/tI/s21106/a/1">Pub. L. 117–58, div. B, title I, § 21106(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="2021-11-15">Nov. 15, 2021</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/135/659">135 Stat. 659</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
